# [✓] Standalone output mode
# [✓] Non-root user (nextjs:nodejs)
# [✓] Build-time env vars (ARG)
# [✓] Telemetry disabled
# [✓] Health check configured
# [✓] Static files copied
# [✓] Minimal attack surface (alpine)
